                    oc:contentOrder 2 ;
                    oc:textContent "All templates inline the `App` class from `@modelcontextprotocol/ext-apps` at build time — the iframe's CSP blocks CDN script imports. They're intentionally framework-free; widgets are small enough that React/Vue hydration cost usually isn't worth it." ],
                [ a oc:Paragraph ;
                    oc:blockType "paragraph" ;
                    oc:contentOrder 1 ;
                    oc:textContent "Minimal HTML scaffolds for the common widget shapes. Copy, fill in, ship." ] ;
            oc:hasSubsection [ a oc:Section ;
                    oc:hasContent [ a oc:Paragraph ;
                            oc:blockType "paragraph" ;
                            oc:contentOrder 1 ;
                            oc:textContent "For presenting multiple items (product picks, search results) in a horizontal scroll rail. Patterns that tested well:" ],
                        [ a oc:BulletList ;
                            oc:blockType "bullet_list" ;
                            oc:contentOrder 2 ;
                            oc:hasItem [ a oc:BulletItem ;
                                    oc:blockType "bullet_item" ;
                                    oc:itemOrder 4 ;
                                    oc:itemText "**Silent state via `updateModelContext`** — cart/selection changes should inform Claude without spamming the chat. Reserve `sendMessage` for terminal actions (\"checkout\", \"done\")." ],
                                [ a oc:BulletItem ;
                                    oc:blockType "bullet_item" ;
                                    oc:itemOrder 5 ;
                                    oc:itemText "**Outbound links via `app.openLink`** — `window.open` and `<a target=\"_blank\">` are blocked by the sandbox." ],
                                [ a oc:BulletItem ;
                                    oc:blockType "bullet_item" ;
                                    oc:itemOrder 1 ;
                                    oc:itemText "**Skip nav chevrons** — users know how to scroll. `scroll-snap-type` can cause a few-px-off-flush initial render; omit it and `scrollLeft = 0` after rendering." ],
                                [ a oc:BulletItem ;
                                    oc:blockType "bullet_item" ;
                                    oc:itemOrder 3 ;
                                    oc:itemText "**Put Claude's reasoning in each item** — a `note` field rendered as a small callout on the card gives users the \"why\" inline." ],
                                [ a oc:BulletItem ;
                                    oc:blockType "bullet_item" ;
                                    oc:itemOrder 2 ;
                                    oc:itemText "**Layout-fork by item count** — `items.length === 1` → detail/PDP layout, `> 1` → carousel. Handle in widget JS, keep the tool schema flat." ] ],
                        [ a oc:Paragraph ;
                            oc:blockType "paragraph" ;
                            oc:contentOrder 4 ;
                            oc:textContent "**Images:** the iframe CSP blocks remote `img-src`. Fetch thumbnails server-side in the tool handler, embed as `data:` URLs in the JSON payload, and render from those. Add `referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\"` as a fallback." ],
                        [ a oc:CodeExample ;
                            oc:blockType "code_block" ;
                            oc:codeContent """<style>
  .rail { display: flex; gap: 10px; overflow-x: auto; padding: 12px; scrollbar-width: none; }
  .rail::-webkit-scrollbar { display: none; }
  .card { flex: 0 0 220px; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 6px; padding: 10px; }
  .thumb-box { aspect-ratio: 1 / 1; display: grid; place-items: center; background: #f7f8f8; }
  .thumb { max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; object-fit: contain; }
  .note { font-size: 12px; color: #666; border-left: 3px solid orange; padding: 2px 8px; margin: 8px 0; }
</style>
<div class="rail" id="rail"></div>
""" ;
